Collections.rule:
Individual: @A* (mm:namespace="http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg#")
Types: onto:Event
Annotations:
    dc:creator patrik,
    dc:created "2024-06-14T15:40:40",
    rdfs:label @B*,
    rdfs:isDefinedBy "http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg"
Facts:
   onto:hasCode @A*,
   onto:hasName @B*,
   onto:hasEventDate @C*(xsd:dateTime),
   onto:hasLocation @D*(mm:EntityIRI)

Individual: @A* (mm:namespace="http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg#")
Types: onto:Person
Annotations:
    dc:creator patrik,
    dc:created "2024-06-14T15:40:40",
    rdfs:label @B*,
    rdfs:isDefinedBy "http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg"
Facts:
   onto:hasCode @A*,
   onto:hasName @B*,
   onto:attendedEvent @C*(mm:EntityIRI),
   onto:isRelatedTo @D*(mm:EntityIRI)

Individual: @A* (mm:namespace="http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg#")
Types: onto:Location
Annotations:
    dc:creator patrik,
    dc:created "2024-06-14T15:40:40",
    rdfs:label @B*,
    rdfs:isDefinedBy "http://www.isws.org/hufflepuff/kg"
Facts:
   onto:hasCode @A*,
   onto:hasName @B*
